name: VERGE-NATIVE EGG
description:
Art and Sound by Mike Neff. 8.8.2021

Verge-native eggs are the rugged and utilitarian apparatus born of necessity in the hidden places nearer the Void. Warm to the touch and surprisingly light-weight, these synthetic wombs carry the last hope of those that now walk in darkness. Their unique audio signature, while harsh and mechanical to most, says much to those who know how to listen. . . .
